[30;1m177 | [0m[35m        if 0.0 < self.step < 1.0:[0m

[30;1m48 | [0m[35m    can be visually diagnosed by visualizers at every point in the pipeline.[0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m50 | [0m[35m    Parameters[0m
[30;1m51 | [0m[35m    ----------[0m
